{"tid":106053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果今年將開始在印度生產 iPhone","createTime":"2017-02-03T10:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T07:09:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8cff9ad7ca6ac3d127ded4b398e344167bd086","tid":106053,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 印度地方政府官員表示,蘋果公司今年將開始在印度製造 iPhone。《法新社》報導,蘋果還沒有證實這項計畫,但執行長庫克本周表示,蘋果有意在印度「大筆投資」,因印度經濟好轉,帶來充分的成長機會。<br />\n<br />\n印度南部卡納塔卡省(Karnataka)資訊科技與生物科技部長卡爾基(Priyank Kharge)向《法新社》指:「我們與蘋果達成協議,我們預期他們4月底前會在卡納塔卡省展開生產作業。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱,新作業可能是組裝國內市場的 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n據研究機構 Canalys,蘋果在印度只有2%的市場佔有率,遠低於三星的23%。有專家表示,在當地製造可以減少公司成本,售價也會因此下降。 (BC)"},{"pid":"b0e69c9a7fe2c23360a0b53ef3f39a1ef0163ee4","tid":106053,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53408b1399c6ef7705b1bf5a5f3b3f7948935966","tid":106053,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"部機有咖哩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9205ad8208fd65f5653e50d2ebf8bf3587c12b22","tid":106053,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"支那仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dca7ab077b473e64be28094066343025139736b","tid":106053,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9164f4f361e49fdca578e8d98bc753dd97597299","tid":106053,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"有無外掛開？"},{"pid":"bbb988d8e967d5ba481bd8c6ff7d25e2d582